= MODULE

xen 

= DESCRIPTION

This is the xen module.
Configure and manage the Xen

== Supported Platforms

* Debian
* Redhat and others: not  tested yet)

== Main classes

* xen($arg) :: Install and configure xen

== Sample Usage

     import xen
     [...]
     class { 'xen':
           arg => 'val'
     }

